txt.en: Keteph wants you to collect five loaves of rye bread for him. He intends to try to infuse his latest recipe with a different bread from the north. Rye bread requires a cook proficient in Ironfold cooking. Seek out a cook with this skill or trade for the bread at the auction house.

Keteph sniffs the bread deeply.

'Ah, that is a richer scent.'

He squeezes the bread and it crunches a bit under the pressure.

'Oh, that is a surprise! A good, thick crust. Yes, I think that this shall do nicely.'
You have five loaves of rye to deliver to Keteph in the Swain's Guild-hall in Umbar BaharbÃªl.
Keteph is undeterred by his failure and looks for a different bread he heard of from the North, rye. He requested that you collect several loaves of rye bread so he may try his recipe again.

'Failure is the first step on the road to success, friend. I will yet uncover the proper bread from the north to use with my latest dish.

'In fact, I have another idea. I hear there is a bread prized in the north that is darker in colour and filled with flavour from spices baked directly into the bread. I desire to try this bread next.

'Can you acquire five loaves of rye bread for me?'
Infusion from the North: A Different Bread
'Have you found enough rye bread for me?'
Deliver the rye nread to Keteph at the Swain's Guild-hall
'I will try the recipe again with a different bread. I am told that the rye bread of the north is tasty and distinct in colour. Can you obtain five loaves for me?'
